des: Calgary’s only radio station designed for all those people who either grew up with the fun music of the 90s, or just love those great songs. Plus, we mix in all the big hits right up to today. The 90s & NOW! An upbeat, fun to listen to radio station with everything from those flashy 90s boy bands, sing-a-long guitar pop, girl power joy and the biggest superstar hits right up to today.C97.7 is a Hot AC radio station from Calgary, Alberta, Canada.
